A celebratory event, including presentations by the winners and a featured speaker, will take place at the 2024 ALA Annual Conference in June 2024 in San Diego. Carnegie Medal winners each receive $5,000. Forty-five books (21 fiction, 24 nonfiction) were selected for the 2024 Andrew Carnegie Medals for Excellence in Fiction and Nonfiction Longlist.
